{"tid":2341521,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"袁國勇信任科興疫苗嗎？ - 馮睎乾","createTime":"2020-12-26T12:20:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-12-27T04:24:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":3,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fcf4c64f59f05aca215bc425e67b12aeaf7170d0","tid":2341521,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-26T12:20:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201226/FLE2JARVHZAZNAVGP45ULKFZC4/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201226%2FFLE2JARVHZAZNAVGP45ULKFZC4%2F&d=gNEzxY0d91fOO8mfTbt%2FUhD7%2Fo0bOSfVmdYqJtNqH20%3D&h=8e793297\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20201226%2FFLE2JARVHZAZNAVGP45ULKFZC4%2F&h=9cb4d923\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20201226/FLE2JARVHZAZNAVGP45ULKFZC4/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n袁國勇信任科興疫苗嗎？ - 馮睎乾<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/jmKCekx0DfGU7BmpTmg5kp34Rqo=/802x451/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/ETQDJN3RS5BWTN7WGO25H5ZE5Y.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FjmKCekx0DfGU7BmpTmg5kp34Rqo%3D%2F802x451%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FETQDJN3RS5BWTN7WGO25H5ZE5Y.png&h=c895a727&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n昨日《明報》刊出〈廣泛接種仗信任 迅速開展顯決心〉，詳述三種疫苗的利弊，很值得看。作者四人都是港大李嘉誠醫學院微生物學系的教授和助理教授，其中兩位是今年三月發表〈大流行緣起武漢，十七年教訓盡忘〉，被美國學棍抹黑為「種族主義」的龍振邦和袁國勇。經一事，長一智，昨日文章寫得謹慎，但不減春秋筆法。<br />\n<br />\n文章圍繞特區政府購入的三種疫苗，即科興的CoronaVac、AstraZeneca和牛津大學的AZD1222，以及復星和德國BioNTech的Tozinameran BNT162b2，為方便記憶，以下將分別簡稱為國產、牛津和德國疫苗。乍看之下，此文似乎提倡先用國產和德國疫苗，主流媒體（包括蘋果）也這樣報道，但我比較關心細微的用字，而非鳥瞰式印象。<br />\n<br />\n先簡介文章幾個要點。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n讀者最該金睛火眼看清楚的一句，我認為是：「CoronaVac。。。。。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n撇開文章不談，袁國勇本人由五月到十二月都堅持：自己不急於接種，即使接種，也只信任自家研發的港大噴鼻式疫苗（儘管是在長春製造）。「廣泛接種仗信任」，要得到袁國勇「信任」，科興似乎尚未做到。由此可見，即使給〈廣〉文換一個較「惹火」的標題，說「袁國勇指科興疫苗尚未達標」，其實也完全不違作者原意，甚至更能畫龍點睛，顯出隱微的春秋筆法。"},{"pid":"9771cb2b6f5d3f7e06777127b2704406a17901bb","tid":2341521,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T00:33:14.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pigxm/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"df653f19a1b61862098c1c739325eebf954a68ba","tid":2341521,"uid":228143,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T00:42:56.000Z","msg":"出來啦許樹昌"},{"pid":"73ed3b87f7ab4174515f1971b27a46d24d2135f6","tid":2341521,"uid":267494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-27T04:24:23.000Z","msg":"袁國勇其實好撚仆街<br />\n自家製量產版本雖然長春做<br />\n分分鐘佢自已噴既可能係親自做<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n又表明唔會帶頭打疫苗<br />\n明當港共係狗咁撚<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}